title: Grateful Dead - Fillmore West 1969 - The Complete Recordings [FL
description:
Grateful Dead - Fillmore West 1969: The Complete Recordings + Bonus Disc

A 10 CD box set of "every note" played at the four Fillmore West shows from February 27th to March 2nd, 1969. Promoted as "the most significant audio release yet to emerge from the Grateful Dead's vault." Mixed from the 16 track master tapes. Mastered in HDCD. 51 tracks, nearly 10 hours of music, 76 pages booklet. Limited edition release of 10,000 copies. Each show is housed in its own digicase. The four shows and the booklet are in a box. Bonus Disc (#11) also included.
